{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016r6M41aATfQUjTEWZwiL7i","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-25\n     2→\n     3→### 14-1-retro-to-sprint-pipeline-epic-td — code-review (2026-03-25T01:59:00Z)\n     4→\n     5→- HIGH (fixed): `generateSlug('')` returns `''`, creating malformed TD story keys\n     6→- HIGH (fixed): `backlogAppended` reports items as persisted when `projectRoot` is omitted\n     7→- HIGH (fixed): `wordOverlap` exceeds 1.0 with duplicate words, breaking dedup contract\n     8→- MEDIUM (fixed): Missing test for no-projectRoot path\n     9→- LOW (unfixed): `getExistingTdTitles` reconstructs titles from slugs, losing fidelity\n    10→- LOW (unfixed): `createTdStory` implicitly creates `epic-TD` via spread+override without `ensureEpicTd` call\n    11→- Coverage gap: No test for `appendToBacklogFile` append-to-existing path or error handling\n    12→- Architecture: state.ts at 543 lines exceeds 300-line limit (pre-existing)\n    13→\n    14→### 14-1-retro-to-sprint-pipeline-epic-td — verification (2026-03-25T02:05:00Z)\n    15→\n    16→- AGENTS.md for src/lib was stale — missing retro-to-sprint.ts entry. Fixed.\n    17→- Disk space critically low (45MB free) — BATS tests failed with \"No space left on device\". Cleared npm cache (2.2GB) to free space.\n    18→- All 10 ACs passed unit-testable verification with direct CLI checks\n    19→- Pre-existing files (state.ts at 543 lines, sprint-yaml.test.ts at 388 lines) exceed 300-line limit but were over before this story\n    20→\n    21→### 14-2-tech-debt-gate-story-selection — create-story (2026-03-25T02:10:00Z)\n    22→\n    23→- Risk: selector.test.ts at 274 lines — adding ~80 lines of new tests may push past 300-line limit, conflicting with AC 9\n    24→- Observation: Original epic had only 2 ACs; expanded to 9 to cover edge cases. Original ACs were underspecified about Tier D gate constraint.\n    25→- Observation: Implementation is ~3 lines in sort comparator. Test changes are the bulk of work.\n    26→\n    27→### 14-2-tech-debt-gate-story-selection — dev-story (2026-03-25T02:20:00Z)\n    28→\n    29→No issues reported. All 11 tasks completed cleanly. 4 lines added to selector.ts, 7 test cases added via it.each. Build, vitest (3664 tests), and BATS (307 tests) all pass.\n    30→\n    31→### 14-2-tech-debt-gate-story-selection — code-review (2026-03-25T02:27:00Z)\n    32→\n    33→- MEDIUM (fixed): AGENTS.md missing TD gate documentation\n    34→- MEDIUM (fixed): Test shorthand variables polluted scope; replaced with typed it.each\n    35→- MEDIUM (fixed): Added case-sensitivity and ready-status test cases (2 new tests, total 3666)\n    36→- LOW (unfixed): selector.ts line 103 comment lacks Decision 6c reference\n    37→- LOW (unfixed): keyToTitle() lowercases \"TD\" to \"Td\" — pre-existing\n    38→- Architecture note: TD gate relies on naming convention (TD- prefix) not structured metadata — accepted tradeoff per Decision 6c\n    39→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"174e0897-5fbc-4ae0-bbc6-8b881d5c7525","uuid":"4eab9214-8c0c-4586-9b7a-59706c602a19","timestamp":"2026-03-24T22:44:56.327Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-25\n\n### 14-1-retro-to-sprint-pipeline-epic-td — code-review (2026-03-25T01:59:00Z)\n\n- HIGH (fixed): `generateSlug('')` returns `''`, creating malformed TD story keys\n- HIGH (fixed): `backlogAppended` reports items as persisted when `projectRoot` is omitted\n- HIGH (fixed): `wordOverlap` exceeds 1.0 with duplicate words, breaking dedup contract\n- MEDIUM (fixed): Missing test for no-projectRoot path\n- LOW (unfixed): `getExistingTdTitles` reconstructs titles from slugs, losing fidelity\n- LOW (unfixed): `createTdStory` implicitly creates `epic-TD` via spread+override without `ensureEpicTd` call\n- Coverage gap: No test for `appendToBacklogFile` append-to-existing path or error handling\n- Architecture: state.ts at 543 lines exceeds 300-line limit (pre-existing)\n\n### 14-1-retro-to-sprint-pipeline-epic-td — verification (2026-03-25T02:05:00Z)\n\n- AGENTS.md for src/lib was stale — missing retro-to-sprint.ts entry. Fixed.\n- Disk space critically low (45MB free) — BATS tests failed with \"No space left on device\". Cleared npm cache (2.2GB) to free space.\n- All 10 ACs passed unit-testable verification with direct CLI checks\n- Pre-existing files (state.ts at 543 lines, sprint-yaml.test.ts at 388 lines) exceed 300-line limit but were over before this story\n\n### 14-2-tech-debt-gate-story-selection — create-story (2026-03-25T02:10:00Z)\n\n- Risk: selector.test.ts at 274 lines — adding ~80 lines of new tests may push past 300-line limit, conflicting with AC 9\n- Observation: Original epic had only 2 ACs; expanded to 9 to cover edge cases. Original ACs were underspecified about Tier D gate constraint.\n- Observation: Implementation is ~3 lines in sort comparator. Test changes are the bulk of work.\n\n### 14-2-tech-debt-gate-story-selection — dev-story (2026-03-25T02:20:00Z)\n\nNo issues reported. All 11 tasks completed cleanly. 4 lines added to selector.ts, 7 test cases added via it.each. Build, vitest (3664 tests), and BATS (307 tests) all pass.\n\n### 14-2-tech-debt-gate-story-selection — code-review (2026-03-25T02:27:00Z)\n\n- MEDIUM (fixed): AGENTS.md missing TD gate documentation\n- MEDIUM (fixed): Test shorthand variables polluted scope; replaced with typed it.each\n- MEDIUM (fixed): Added case-sensitivity and ready-status test cases (2 new tests, total 3666)\n- LOW (unfixed): selector.ts line 103 comment lacks Decision 6c reference\n- LOW (unfixed): keyToTitle() lowercases \"TD\" to \"Td\" — pre-existing\n- Architecture note: TD gate relies on naming convention (TD- prefix) not structured metadata — accepted tradeoff per Decision 6c\n","numLines":39,"startLine":1,"totalLines":39}}}
