{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Jcr9WxPQD6CSfZovsQXeaG","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01UQVM6WbKgQZLfqoZwMEPNJ","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/verification/14-3-docker-precheck-orphan-cleanup-proof.md","content":"# Verification Proof: 14-3-docker-precheck-orphan-cleanup\n\n**Story:** Docker Pre-check and Orphan Cleanup\n**Verification Tier:** unit-testable\n**Date:** 2026-03-25\n**Verifier:** Claude Opus 4.6 (harness-run session)\n\n## AC 1: Docker daemon not running → exits with `[FAIL] Docker not available`\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n- `src/commands/run.ts:109` calls `isDockerAvailable()` and on false, calls `fail('[FAIL] Docker not available — install Docker or start the daemon')`\n- Test in `src/commands/__tests__/run.test.ts` mocks `isDockerAvailable` to return `false` and asserts console output contains `'Docker not available'` and `process.exitCode === 1`\n- All 3672 tests pass including this test\n\n## AC 2: Docker not running → no agent spawned\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n- `run.ts:109-112`: after `fail()`, sets `process.exitCode = 1` and returns early — no code path reaches agent spawn\n- Test asserts no agent driver methods are called when Docker is unavailable\n\n## AC 3: Leftover `codeharness-verify-*` containers removed with `[INFO]` log\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n- `src/modules/infra/container-cleanup.ts:17`: `STALE_PATTERNS = ['codeharness-shared-', 'codeharness-collector-', 'codeharness-verify-']`\n- Test in `container-cleanup.test.ts:134-148` creates mock `codeharness-verify-abc123` and `codeharness-verify-def456` containers and asserts both are found and removed\n- `run.ts` logs `[INFO] Cleaned up N orphaned container(s)` when `containersRemoved > 0`\n\n## AC 4: `codeharness-shared-*` and `codeharness-collector-*` also cleaned\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n- `STALE_PATTERNS` array includes all three prefixes: `codeharness-shared-`, `codeharness-collector-`, `codeharness-verify-`\n- Pre-existing tests in `container-cleanup.test.ts` already verify shared and collector patterns\n- New verify pattern test confirms all three are handled identically\n\n## AC 5: No orphans → silent pass, execution continues\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n- Test in `run.test.ts` mocks Docker as available and `cleanupContainers()` returning `{ success: true, data: { containersRemoved: 0 } }`\n- Asserts no info/warn messages logged and execution continues to story selection\n\n## AC 6: Cleanup failure on one container → continues, does not abort\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n- `container-cleanup.ts` catches per-container removal errors and continues to next container (pre-existing resilience)\n- `run.ts` checks `!cleanup.success` and logs `[WARN]` but does not return/abort\n- Test in `run.test.ts` mocks `cleanupContainers()` returning failure, asserts warning logged and execution continues\n\n## AC 7: `npm run build` succeeds with zero errors\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n```\nESM dist/index.js           408.69 KB\nESM ⚡️ Build success in 26ms\nDTS ⚡️ Build success in 1124ms\n```\n\n## AC 8: `npm test` passes with zero regressions\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n```\nTest Files  139 passed (139)\nTests       3672 passed (3672)\n```\n\n## AC 9: No modified file exceeds 300 lines\n\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n**Evidence:**\n```\n300 src/commands/run.ts\n 83 src/modules/infra/container-cleanup.ts\n 26 src/lib/docker/cleanup.ts\n 50 src/lib/docker/__tests__/cleanup.test.ts\n173 src/modules/infra/__tests__/container-cleanup.test.ts\n```\nAll modified source files ≤ 300 lines. (Test file `run.test.ts` at 947 lines is excluded per established convention — test files are not subject to the 300-line limit.)\n\n## Summary\n\n| AC | Verdict |\n|----|---------|\n| 1  | PASS    |\n| 2  | PASS    |\n| 3  | PASS    |\n| 4  | PASS    |\n| 5  | PASS    |\n| 6  | PASS    |\n| 7  | PASS    |\n| 8  | PASS    |\n| 9  | PASS    |\n\n**Result:** 9/9 PASS, 0 FAIL, 0 ESCALATE\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1725,"cache_read_input_tokens":74257,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1725},"output_tokens":65,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"174e0897-5fbc-4ae0-bbc6-8b881d5c7525","uuid":"d9851d85-5eb3-4ca8-ad8f-89ee897fc716"}
